          "description": "The Endocrinology department is a joke. I've seen Dr. Pal and she complained to me that I don't go see her much when I can't make a early appointment with her because when you make a appointment you will see Dr. Pal in 5-6 months sometimes even more. I mostly saw Sylvaine most of the time but she didn't know what she was doing. I did whatever she told me but it nothing worked because my blood sugar was still high and she told me to increase Tresiba every week. Is she insane??? You are supposed to increase Tresiba once a month not once a week. If you need to see a Endocrinologist go somewhere else you won't be happy here.",
